{"tid":688412,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU為什麼這麼漂亮呢？今天就來帶你一起分析關於IU的長相","createTime":"2018-06-03T07:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T12:28:44.000Z","uid":34643,"like":24,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5a68606c6572ddc7b8e0fac86de8e5ecd8c442","tid":688412,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:56:04.000Z","msg":"IU其實是屬於比較典型的亞洲臉吧，是有點點藏雙的眼皮，也是有點塌的鼻梁，然後呢屬於微胖的鵝蛋臉。雖然很多人都過說她整容，可是在我來看她是真的沒怎麼整。首先是在發型方面。iu其實也是鵝蛋臉型，鼻子的話比較塌，但是她的眼睛真的很漂亮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t11.baidu.com/it/u=1355943808,3248337758&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=1152&amp;s=E8B117D1021841D4989960950300C0C3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft11.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1355943808%2C3248337758%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D1152%26s%3DE8B117D1021841D4989960950300C0C3&h=aed8be7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以我認為的話，應該是要突出眼睛部位，所以是比較適合露出額頭的，而不怎麼適合留厚重的劉海的，尤其是在齊劉海這種非常的考驗五官立體感造型。如果我們對比的話，就會很明顯的發現，無劉海的樣子要看起來甜美了許多，是因為沒有劉海的話就可以突出眼睛漂亮的優勢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=587966301,89399938&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=1139&amp;s=08F2ED126F236B05266044E10300C0A3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D587966301%2C89399938%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D1139%26s%3D08F2ED126F236B05266044E10300C0A3&h=b258dff4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後將視覺的重心全部集中在中間的部位-眼睛，從而也就弱化了鼻子塌的劣勢。另外呢，iu的眉毛是很精致的類型，並不是爛大街的那種一字眉，而是說稍稍有點八字眉的樣子，而這種明顯會更引人憐愛。而且呢iu我個人覺得應該是長發勝過短發的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://t10.baidu.com/it/u=1608185160,377631112&amp;fm=173&amp;app=25&amp;f=JPEG?w=640&amp;h=1138&amp;s=BB0ACF0019FA479ACC1CA8DE0300C0A0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft10.baidu.com%2Fit%2Fu%3D1608185160%2C377631112%26fm%3D173%26app%3D25%26f%3DJPEG%3Fw%3D640%26h%3D1138%26s%3DBB0ACF0019FA479ACC1CA8DE0300C0A0&h=f3757e07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然說短發可以增添她像精靈一樣可愛的氣質，可是如果是長發的話就不僅可愛了，還多了那麼一絲嫵媚與甜美風。至於在發色方面的話，iu是比較白的類型，所以的話，各種顏色還算是hold住的。但是，如果要說最適合的話，我想還是巧克力色吧。那麼除了發型之外，IU也很擅長用配飾來增加自己的甜美元素。而點晴之筆就是耳釘。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img2.ruliweb.com/mypi/gup/a/14/7/o/6386025291.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg2.ruliweb.com%2Fmypi%2Fgup%2Fa%2F14%2F7%2Fo%2F6386025291.jpg&h=5e2e7714&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n配飾簡直可以說是心機一筆。尤其是這種銀色和水晶色的耳釘，能夠經常的和其他部位的搭配去相互照應。除此之外呢，iu的身材是屬於比較嬌小的類型，但是這一點可能是優勢但也有可能是劣勢。優勢的話就是妹子是很瘦的，所以像穿衣服走個甜美或者是小清新路線都是游刃有余的。但是劣勢的話大概就是，因為身高不夠，所以不怎麼有氣場吧。那麼呢為了避免這一劣勢，IU會選擇穿短款的裙子或者短褲，從而來增強視覺上腿長的一個效果。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://file3.instiz.net/data/file3/2018/03/01/b/2/d/b2d9cd1c4c8da014dd6b21de505b5685.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffile3.instiz.net%2Fdata%2Ffile3%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2Fb%2F2%2Fd%2Fb2d9cd1c4c8da014dd6b21de505b5685.jpg&h=03dc5ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同時呢也可以多了一分可愛與俏皮風。而且呢我還發現IU真的是各種短裙阿，比如說夏天就是像短裙襯衫，而冬天呢就是短裙，然後是過膝靴，外面再加一件大衣。IU妹子的長相是那種看起來非常的甜美，然後讓人感覺到很舒服的這種類型。雖然說她沒有深邃的雙眼皮，也沒有高鼻梁，甚至也沒有瓜子臉，尖下巴，但是她給我們的整體感覺是很和諧的樣子。"},{"pid":"503b44b8c3e8c0d9cbb2436614d98fbd93ed15db","tid":688412,"uid":94828,"like":21,"dislike":49,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T07:57:28.000Z","msg":"成個唐氏綜合症咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6b57c115e90840215ca43e99ac97cdce275568","tid":688412,"uid":133224,"like":17,"dislike":21,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:02:13.000Z","msg":"真心理解唔到有幾靚<br />\n比盡中上"},{"pid":"2f01f266c7bdba9a4f107edb95a84bbed8cb86a9","tid":688412,"uid":7854,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:03:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/22/001718_85dd30aba7b173c453f97c178af0519a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F22%2F001718_85dd30aba7b173c453f97c178af0519a.jpg&h=e158eab3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecf1cc270942f7111fccf369dc4c88929b1d9713","tid":688412,"uid":104658,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:07:21.000Z","msg":"話唔靚個d 可唔可以貼張真係靚女嘅圖睇睇<br />\n<br />\n我想見識下你眼中乜叫靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"512b6a1047f18d701e3fd02801a7bc8ea6fce7e1","tid":688412,"uid":54929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602df600ec945c6726665e365d5010cd087e6e40","tid":688412,"uid":33059,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:12:25.000Z","msg":"淫底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c38c4e3b6a59721ae5dad3a925bf079bde1950","tid":688412,"uid":131622,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T08:51:24.000Z","msg":"一白遮三醜"},{"pid":"d34109d8b4625d337e2185b0123d573d52d65852","tid":688412,"uid":34643,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i3.ruliweb.com/img/16/07/17/155f9130a4f46c91a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi3.ruliweb.com%2Fimg%2F16%2F07%2F17%2F155f9130a4f46c91a.jpg&h=a70e9b90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i2.ruliweb.com/img/16/07/17/155f91440d346c91a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.ruliweb.com%2Fimg%2F16%2F07%2F17%2F155f91440d346c91a.jpg&h=b4165d9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"23af3a198e5deb4bdd8d527de4874a8fa926f5a6","tid":688412,"uid":68553,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:33:30.000Z","msg":"短髮真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd19a04ec07b072e9de7c6508437f5a81c93081","tid":688412,"uid":71497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T09:47:00.000Z","msg":"白滑<br />\n有腳<br />\n小籠包<br />\n乳頭"},{"pid":"f48f257f7c2ab03e4917a0805fb9920537e3780d","tid":688412,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":